def maximize_card_value(N: int, K: int) -> int:
    digits = [int(x) for x in str(N)]
    i = 1
    while i < K:
        min_digit = min(digits)
        if min_digit == 9:
            break
        min_index = digits.index(min_digit)
        digits[min_index] = min_digit + 1
        i += 1
    product = 1
    for digit in digits:
        product *= digit
    return product
